      <T n="text">0xF1683AF3<!--String: "The <b><font color='#199C2C'>Family Tree</font></b> has been updated to display a lot of new and detailed information!\n\nYou can now keep track of which Sims are connected as part of the same <b><font color='#199C2C'>Dynasty</font></b>, and see each Sim's Dynasty Crest right by their portrait. The Head of a Dynasty and the Heir of a Dynasty will also have a unique icon in the top right corner.\n<b><font color='#199C2C'>Noble Sims</font></b> also have a nobility emblem around their portrait representative of their Noble Title.\n\nYou can access a Sim's Family Tree via their <b><font color='#199C2C'>Simology panel</font></b>, or by interacting with the new <b><font color='#199C2C'>Family Tree Tapestry object</font></b>."--></T>
